          {
            "heading": "Elevated privacy, effortless comfort.",
            "body": "PADORA is a thoughtfully crafted collaborative soft-seating system that elevates user experience in evolving workplaces. It seamlessly blends comfort, aesthetics, and utility to create modular seating islands, booths, and breakout zones."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Adaptable to diverse workstyles, PADORA transitions effortlessly between open lounges for collaboration, enclosed setups for focused work, and clustered arrangements for team zones. Integrated nook seating offers dedicated spaces for solo tasks or casual breaks."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Freestanding or seamlessly integrated side tables provide convenient surfaces for devices, notes, or essentials, enhancing everyday usability without disrupting the seating layout."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Thoughtfully placed hooks offer a simple solution for hanging bags or coats, keeping the space organized, clutter-free, and user-centric."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Built-in electrical options ensure easy access to power, supporting seamless device usage and uninterrupted productivity in collaborative and focused settings."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Available in multiple configurations, the system adapts effortlessly to diverse layouts and workstyles, supporting collaboration, focus, and seamless spatial planning."
